here. 
 
 
POLITICAL, SECURITY, HUMAN RIGHTS 
 
 
2. Ozgur Gundem / Sevim Yetkiner was re-elected as 
the new head of the Mus Human Rights 
Organization. 
 
 
3. Ozgur Gundem / Z.Y, a man released from Urfa 
