"23991","12/13/2004 15:31","04ADANA154","Consulate Adana","UNCLASSIFIED//FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY","04ANKARA6848","This record is a partial extract of the original cable. The full text of the original cable is not available.

","UNCLAS SECTION 01 OF 02 ADANA 000154 
 
