"24828","1/3/2005 7:48","05ADANA2","Consulate Adana","UNCLASSIFIED//FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY","05ADANA160","This record is a partial extract of the original cable. The full text of the original cable is not available.

","UNCLAS ADANA 000002 
 
